Package de.frauas.dronesimulation.app.dronelist

Class DroneList

java.lang.Object
de.frauas.dronesimulation.app.dronelist.DroneList
public class DroneList extends Object
This class represents a single drone. Each drone has an id, a drone type, a creation time, a serial number, a carriage weight, a carriage type, and a list of drone dynamics.
